      "instruction": "<p>Fill each<strong> hot dog bun </strong>with a <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>hot dog</strong>, then top with some <strong>satay sauce</strong>, <strong>remaining chopped peanuts</strong>, <strong>coriander leaves </strong>and some of the <strong>lime-pickled mooli slaw </strong>– these are your <strong>meat-free peanut satay hot dogs</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>paprika lime fries</strong>, the <strong>remaining lime-pickled mooli slaw</strong> <strong>and any remaining satay sauce </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
